:: Configure recycling for ASP.NET 1.1 App Pool\ncscript.exe adsutil.vbs SET W3SVC/AppPools/ASP.NET1.1AppPool/RecycleWorkerProcesses true\ncscript.exe adsutil.vbs SET W3SVC/AppPools/ASP.NET1.1AppPool/PeriodicRestartTime 120\n\n:: Configure recycling for ASP.NET 2.0 App Pool\ncscript.exe adsutil.vbs SET W3SVC/AppPools/ASP.NET2.0AppPool/RecycleWorkerProcesses true\ncscript.exe adsutil.vbs SET W3SVC/AppPools/ASP.NET2.0AppPool/PeriodicRestartTime 120